## SimpleExpressionNode.isRuntimeConstant property

some expressions (e.g. transformAssetUrls import identifiers) are constant, but cannot be stringified because they must be first evaluated at runtime.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
isRuntimeConstant?: boolean;
```
